Update System Packages: First, ensure that your package list is up to date by running:
install ansible on ubuntu
Install Software Properties Common: This package allows you to add the necessary Ansible PPA:
sudo apt update
sudo apt install software-properties-common
Add Ansible PPA: Add the Ansible repository to your system:
sudo add-apt-repository --yes --update ppa:ansible/ansible
Install Ansible: Now, install Ansible with the following command:
sudo apt install ansible
Verify Installation: To confirm Ansible is installed correctly, check the version:
ansible --version

https://www.cherryservers.com/blog/install-ansible-ubuntu
